      "brollTrim": null,
      "text": "MemWal plus plus — hybrid verifiable memory for autonomous agents. Built for Sui Overflow and the Walrus track. Local speed, Walrus truth, on-chain economy."
    },
    {
      "id": "02-problem",
      "slide": 2,
      "file": "02-problem.mp3",
      "durationSec": 14,
      "timelineStartSec": 14.0,
      "timelineEndSec": 28.0,
      "targetSec": 14,
      "broll": null,
      "brollTrim": null,
      "text": "Agents forget between sessions. Opaque databases can't prove what was remembered. Marketplaces need portable memory — not screenshots. And inference can't wait on the network every token."
    },
    {
      "id": "03-solution",
      "slide": 3,
      "file": "03-solution.mp3",
      "durationSec": 15,
      "timelineStartSec": 28.0,
      "timelineEndSec": 43.0,
      "targetSec": 15,
      "broll": null,
      "brollTrim": null,
      "text": "MemWal plus plus is three layers: SQLite local-first, MemWal to Walrus for durable blobs, and Sui Move for packs, marketplace, and WAL bounties. Redact and score before anything leaves the machine."
    },
    {
      "id": "04-flow",
      "slide": 4,
      "file": "04-flow.mp3",
      "durationSec": 16,
      "timelineStartSec": 43.0,
      "timelineEndSec": 59.0,
      "targetSec": 16,
      "broll": "docs/diagrams/memwalpp-merged-architecture.svg",
      "brollTrim": null,
      "text": "The path is explicit: local store, redaction, quality gate, then remember to Walrus. Every promoted row gets a walrus blob id — the same id Sui bounties reference on fulfillment."
    },
